title: Ben.10.Green.Repack
description:
Ben.10.Green.Repack

Genre: Action
Developer: Torus Games 
Publisher: Outright Games


About This Game

It’s Hero Time!
Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max once again have their cross-country road trip in the Rust Bucket cut short by super villains and their evil, world-threatening plans. 

As Ben Tennyson, it’s up to you to save the world. Take on some of Ben’s most infamous enemies, including Zombozo, Queen Bee, and the Weatherheads. Unlock and transform into all ten of Ben’s incredible alien forms. Use each alien’s powerful combat moves – including Ultimate Attacks - to lay the beat-down on enemies with devastating combos, and solve puzzles with each alien’s unique abilities as you unravel exciting new stories in three all-new playable episodes.


System Requirements

Minimum:
OS: 7 / 8 / 10
Processor: Intel Core 2 Quad Q6600 (2.4 GHz) or AMD equivalent
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: GeForce GT 430 (1024 MB)/ Radeon HD 6850 (1024 MB)
DirectX: Version 9.0c
Storage: 3 GB available space
Sound Card: DirectX compatible
Recommended:
OS: 10
Processor: Intel i5, 4 x 2.6 GHz or AMD equivalent
Memory: 4 GB RAM
Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 480 or ATI Radeon HD 5850 or better, 1Gb RAM
DirectX: Version 11
Storage: 5 GB available space
Sound Card: DirectX compatible

After download is done:
- open Ben.10.Green.Repack(executable file)
- choose location ,
- click install ,
- wait until is done 
- play game from desktop shortcut 
or Run ...Prodigy.exe from the game install path
